products.title: Botanical Garden Seaspray Blue Curtain
products.description: Lilies, bluebells, peonies, and all things flowery make up this botanical curtain. With dragonflies, busy bees and delicate butterflies dotting this seaspray blue curtain, with splashes of warm yellows and greens, this curtain will look at home in your kitchen, office or bedroom. At swift direct blinds, quality is important to us, which is why your new curtain comes with a fabulous five year guarantee, for extra peace of mind.
